Package: LinearRegress
Type: Package
Title: Simple and Extended Linear Regression for the Boston Housing Dataset
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Calvin Kristianto Thayono (120040029), Yahia Ezzat (120040030), Yuhang Li(117010141)
Maintainer: Calvin Kristianto Thayono (120040029) <120040029@link.cuhk.edu.cn>
Description: This package provides functions to perform simple and extended linear regression on the Boston Housing dataset. 
             It includes preprocessing, model training, prediction, evaluation, and cross-validation capabilities. 
             The package supports standard linear regression, ridge regression, and LASSO for a comprehensive analysis of the dataset.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
